### NFT API Example Requests - FULL COLLECTION DEPLOYMENT
### Use with REST Client extension in VS Code or copy to curl

### 1. Check Wallet Info
GET http://localhost:3000/wallet-info

###

### 2. Deploy NFT Collection (DO THIS FIRST!)
POST http://localhost:3000/deploy-collection
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "collectionName": "My NFT Collection",
  "collectionDescription": "A collection of unique digital collectibles",
  "collectionImage": "https://picsum.photos/800/800"
}

### WAIT 30 SECONDS AFTER DEPLOYMENT BEFORE MINTING!

###

### 3. Mint NFT from Collection (Will appear in wallets!)
POST http://localhost:3000/mint-nft
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Awesome NFT #1",
  "description": "This NFT is minted from a real collection and will show in Tonkeeper!",
  "image": "https://picsum.photos/500/500"
}

###

### 4. Get Collection Info
GET http://localhost:3000/collection-info

###
